title: John Fitzgerald Kennedy National Historic Site: Current Conditions
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Basic Information     Current Conditions             Alerts & Conditions         Alerts    Information        Limited Access to Beals Street  Alert 1 , Severity ,information ,, Limited Access to Beals Street  For the next week, there will be limited access to Beals Street because of local construction. Visitors may park on adjacent streets- Stedmen and Naples- for up to two hours.
